    "description": "Our take on classic kedgeree is a smoky stunner. You'll simmer smoked basa and rice in a fragrant curry stock till tender. Load it with peas and spinach before serving up with a soft-boiled egg on top. Delicious. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
